 >| [ MP_TAC (Q.SPECL [`f`, `f'`, `x`, `cball(x:real,e)`, `e`]
              DIFFERENTIAL_COMPONENT_NEG_AT_MAXIMUM),
      MP_TAC (Q.SPECL [`f`, `f'`, `x`, `cball(x:real,e)`, `e`]
